# AI Projects (Python)

This repository contains two beginner-level Python projects focused on chatbot logic and computer vision.

---

## 🤖 Project 1: AI Chatbot

A simple rule-based chatbot built using Python.

### Features
- Text-based interaction
- Keyword-based responses
- Uses loops and dictionaries

### How to run

python chatbot.py

---

## 🎥 Project 2: Face Detection

A real-time face detection system using OpenCV.

### Features
- Uses webcam to capture video
- Detects faces in real-time
- Draws bounding boxes around faces

### How to run

python face_detection.py

---

## 🧠 Technologies Used
- Python
- OpenCV

